REGRESSION_T-015.md

# === Capstone Internal Documentation ===
docs/capstone/
docs/operations/
docs/security/
docs/api
docs/architecture

# === Validation & Test Scripts (Non-Essential) ===
validate_t006.sh
validate_t004_t005.sh

# === Keep Essential Files ===
!README.md
!.env.example
!.gitkeep
!Makefile
!.dockerignore
!Dockerfile
!docker-compose.yml
!pytest.ini
!pyproject.toml
!package.json
!tsconfig.json
!next.config.ts
!postcss.config.mjs
!vitest.config.ts

# Downloaded model weights (large files, not tracked)
models/
